name: savings-multiplied-materialize
description: 1. Create new project on Github. Do not initialize with a Readme, gitignore, or a License. 2. Make a directory on your local machine for the project. 3. copy all files from this template into the project directory.     * `cp -r c8-grunt-template/ new-project` 4. `npm init` and `bower init` 5. Add npm dependencies to the `package.json` file and then run `npm install`
